Reasoning: The paper discusses the role of AI in Adaptive eLearning Systems, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The use of AI in content aggregation and personalization also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The risks and opportunities involved in AES also touch on cybersecurity (cs.CY) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
